\u00f3 oldal a koronav\u00edrusr\u00f3l |date=25 March 2020 |publisher=Cabinet Office of the Prime Minister |language=hu |access-date=25 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317001549/https://koronavirus.gov.hu/ |archive-date=17 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BLR}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Belarus|Belarus]]\n|700\n|13\n|53\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://spkc.gov.lv/lv/aktualitates/get/nid/757 |title=Aktualit\u0101tes - Slim\u012bbu profilakses un kontroles centrs |website=spkc.gov.lv |access-date=11 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313183500/https://spkc.gov.lv/lv/aktualitates/get/nid/757 |archive-date=13 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BIH}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n|674\n|29\n|47\n|\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|MKD}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in North Macedonia|North Macedonia]]\n|570\n|21\n|27\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://makfax.com.mk/makedonija/%d0%b2%d0%b8%d0%b4%d0%b5%d0%be-%d1%83%d1%88%d1%82%d0%b5-%d1%88%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82-%d0%bb%d0%b8%d1%86%d0%b0-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%b7%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%b8%d0%b2%d0%bd%d0%b8-%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d0%ba%d0%be%d1%80%d0%be/ |title=\u0423\u0448\u0442\u0435 \u0448\u0435\u0441\u0442 \u043b\u0438\u0446\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u0437\u0438\u0442\u0438\u0432\u043d\u0438 \u043d\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441, \u0432\u043a\u0443\u043f\u043d\u043e 18 |date=14 March 2020 |website=Makfax |language=mk |access-date=14 March 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316040526/https://makfax.com.mk/makedonija/%d0%b2%d0%b8%d0%b4%d0%b5%d0%be-%d1%83%d1%88%d1%82%d0%b5-%d1%88%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82-%d0%bb%d0%b8%d1%86%d0%b0-%d0%bf%d0%be%d0%b7%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%b8%d0%b2%d0%bd%d0%b8-%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d0%ba%d0%be%d1%80%d0%be/ |archive-date=16 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Flagicon|BUL}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Bulgaria|Bulgaria]]\n|565\n|22\n|42\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=http:/