re]], [[New York City]], New York, U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|14\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|14\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Tim Noble\n|TKO\n|3 (6), {{small|1:04}}\n|Nov 10, 1993\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Broadway By the Bay Theater, Atlantic City, New Jersey, U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|13\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|13\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Danny Blake\n|PTS\n|6\n|Jul 10, 1993\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Fernwood Resort, Bushkill, Pennsylvania, U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|12\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|12\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Bruce Johnson\n|TKO\n|1 (6), {{small|1:36}}\n|[[Riddick Bowe vs. Jesse Ferguson|May 22, 1993]]\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Robert F. Kennedy Memorial Stadium]], [[Washington, D.C.]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|11\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|11\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Ron Gullette\n|TKO\n|1 (6), {{small|1:52}}\n|Mar 25, 1993\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Broadway By the Bay Theater]], [[Atlantic City, New Jersey]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|10\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|10\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Robert Pagan Perez\n|KO\n|1\n|Dec 9, 1992\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Newark, New Jersey]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|9\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|9\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Rocky Bentley\n|{{abbr|PTS|Points decision}}\n|4\n|Dec 4, 1992\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Fernwood Resort, [[Bushkill, Pennsylvania]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|8\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|8\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Rick Honeycutt\n|TKO\n|1\n|Nov 21, 1992\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Miami, Florida]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|7\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|7\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}}Tony Simpson\n|TKO\n|1\n|Nov 13, 1992\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|[[Revere, Massachusetts]], U.S.}}\n|\n|-\n|6\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|6\u20130\n|